Package arrayGenerator

Tools for generator arrays with various properties.
Version:
September 2020
Author:
Hugh Osborne
  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    ArrayGenerator
    Defines the interface for classes that generate arrays of ints
    ListingGenerator
    A Listing is a special type of Array, in which an array of size n will contain each of the values 0..n-1 exactly once.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ArrayGeneratorTest
    A tester class for ArrayGenerators.
    CleverRandomListingGenerator  
    CleverRandomListingGeneratorTest  
    ListingGeneratorTest
    A tester class for ListingGenerators.
    RandomListingGenerator
    An array generator that generates an array containing the values 0..n in random order.
    RandomListingGeneratorTest
    A tester class for RandomListingGenerators.
    SimpleRandomListingGenerator
    Completes the implementation of random listing generator, using a simple randomising method.
    SimpleRandomListingGeneratorTest
    A tester class for SortedListingGenerators.
    SortedListingGenerator
    A simple array generator, that generates a sorted array [0,1,2,..,n]
    SortedListingGeneratorTest
    A tester class for SortedListingGenerators.
